T*
(- Regenerate emissions outputs with python3 Src/Main/esim.py.) Tj
T*
(- Rebuild whitepaper PDFs from updated sources.) Tj
T*
(- Update any docs that expose user-facing values \(confirmations, fee floor, pool routing,) Tj
T*
(maturity, supply figures\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(When adding a new doc:) Tj
T*
(- place it in the most relevant section above,) Tj
T*
(- include date and scope,) Tj
T*
(- include code path references when making consensus or security claims,) Tj
T*
(- avoid copying stale policy snippets from older drafts.) Tj
T*
() Tj
